quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,38,"yeh haal dekh kar Zikria ne apne Rab ko puraka"" parvar-digaar! apni qudrat se mujhe naik aulaad ataa kar to hi dua suneney wala hai """
3,39,"jawab mein firshton ne aawaz di, jab ke woh mahaRab mein khara namaz parh raha tha, ke"" Allah tujhe yahya ki khush khaberi deta hai woh Allah ki taraf se aik farmaan ki tasdeeq karne o ila ban kar aeye ga is mein sardari o buzurgi ki shaan hogi kamaal darja ka Zabit hoga nabuwat se Sarfraz hoga aur صالحین mein shumaar kya jaye ga """
3,40,"Zikria ne kaha,"" parvar-digaar! bhala mere haan larka kahan se hoga, mein to boorha ho chuka hon aur meri biwi banjh hai"" jawab mila,"" aisa hi hoga, Allah jo chahta hai karta hai """
3,41,"arz kya"" maalik! phir koi nishani mere liye muqarrar farma day"" kaha,"" nishani yeh hai ke tum teen din taq logon se ishara ke siwa koi baat cheet nah karo ge ( ya nah krsko ge ) iss douran mein apne Rab ko bohat yaad karna aur subah o shaam is ki tasbeeh karte rehna """
3,42,"phir woh waqt aaya jab maryam se firshton ne aakar kaha,"" ae maryam! Allah ne tujhe bargzida kya aur pakizgee ataa ki aur tamam duniya ki aurton par tujh ko tarjeeh day kar apni khidmat ke liye chunn liya"
3,43,"ae maryam! apne Rab ki tabay farmaan ban kar reh, is ke agay sir bsjod ho, aur jo bande is ke huzoor jhuknay walay hain un ke sath to bhi jhuk ja """
3,44,"ae Muammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! yeh ghaib ki khabrain hain jo hum tum ko wahi ke zareya se bta rahay hain, warna tum uss waqt wahan mojood nah thay jab hekal ke khadim yeh faisla karne ke liye ke maryam ka sir parast kon ho apne apne qalam pheink rahay thay, aur nah tum uss waqt haazir thay, jab unn ke darmain jhagra barpaa tha"
3,45,"aur jab firshton ne kaha,"" ae maryam! Allah tujhe apne aik farmaan ki khush khaberi deta hai uss ka naam maseeh ( hazrat ) Eesa Ibn maryam(alh-e-salam) hoga, duniya aur akhirat mein Muaziz hoga, Allah ke MaqarRab bundon mein shumaar kya jaye ga"
